  "key_logic": [
    "Transaction.calculateOperations(): DFS topological traversal of result packages; compares present vs result to emit Install/Update ops; emits Uninstall ops for removed packages; reorders plugins-first then uninstalls-first",
    "LockTransaction.setResultPackages(): iterates Decisions, extracts positive literals from Pool, splits into all/non-dev buckets (unlockableMap keys = dev packages)",
    "LockTransaction.setNonDevPackages(): second pass after separate non-dev solve; reclassifies packages into dev vs non-dev",
    "LocalRepoTransaction: thin wrapper — present=localRepo.getPackages(), result=lockedRepo.getPackages()"
  ],

